## ⚙️ Prerequisites

* Kubernetes cluster (running)
* kubectl configured
* Helm installed
* StorageClass available in cluster

Check storage class:

```bash
kubectl get sc
```

---

## 📦 Add Helm Repository

```bash
helm repo add sonatype https://sonatype.github.io/helm3-charts/
helm repo update
```

---

## 🏗️ Create Namespace

```bash
kubectl create namespace nexus
```

---

## ⚙️ values.yaml Configuration

### 🔹 Key Configurations

```yaml
nexus:
  imageName: sonatype/nexus3
  tag: "3.68.1"

  resources:
    requests:
      memory: "2Gi"
      cpu: "500m"
    limits:
      memory: "4Gi"
      cpu: "1"

  env:
    - name: INSTALL4J_ADD_VM_PARAMS
      value: "-Xms1g -Xmx2g -XX:MaxDirectMemorySize=2g"

persistence:
  enabled: true
  storageClass: ""   # Uses default StorageClass
  accessMode: ReadWriteOnce
  size: 20Gi

service:
  type: NodePort
  port: 8081
  nodePort: 32000
```

---

## 🚀 Deploy Nexus

```bash
helm install nexus sonatype/nexus-repository-manager \
  -n nexus \
  -f values.yaml
```

---

## 🔄 Upgrade Deployment

```bash
helm upgrade nexus sonatype/nexus-repository-manager \
  -n nexus \
  -f values.yaml
```

---

## 🔍 Verify Deployment

```bash
kubectl get pods -n nexus
kubectl get svc -n nexus
kubectl get pvc -n nexus
```

Expected:

* Pod status: `Running`
* PVC status: `Bound`

