## ⚠️ Troubleshooting

### ❌ PVC Pending

* Check StorageClass
* Set `storageClass: ""` or correct value

### ❌ Image Pull Error

* Ensure image tag is specified

### ❌ Nexus Not Accessible

* Verify NodePort
* Check firewall/security groups

### ❌ Liveness Probe Failed

* Wait 2–5 minutes (Nexus startup time)
* Increase memory if needed

