## 🧠 Best Practices

* Use persistent storage (PVC)
* Allocate minimum 2GB RAM
* Use specific image tag (avoid `latest`)
* Use Ingress for production
* Enable backup strategy

---

## 🔐 Production Recommendations

* Use Ingress + HTTPS
* Configure authentication/LDAP
* Enable Nexus cleanup policies
* Secure with firewall rules
* Monitor using Prometheus/Grafana

